  <brief_title>Effect of the Dietary Supplement SAMe on Blood Homocysteine Levels</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of the Dietary Supplement S-Adenosyl-L-Methionine on Plasma Homocysteine Levels in Healthy Human Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
